{"data":[{"date":"15:04 18/07","title":"Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u00e1n m\u1ecdi t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n \u1edf TBN","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4345","checkdouble":"191518"},{"date":"16:13 18/07","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean sau World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/18/tuyen-thu-nhat-ban-ket-hon-voi-vo-dien-vien-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Erina Mano ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u00f4n c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Gaku Shibasaki. Hai v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ed1ng sau khi k\u1ebft h\u00f4n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ng\u00e0y 16/7, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111a t\u00e0i Erina Mano ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00f4 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Gaku Shibasaki \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u00f4n. Hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGaku Shibasaki hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, sau khi k\u1ebft h\u00f4n, Erina Mano s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c trong showbiz v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng ch\u1ed3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/mano540150008.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Erina Mano v\u00e0 Gaku Shibasaki h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017. Hai v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd chuy\u1ebfn t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ed1ng sau khi k\u1ebft h\u00f4n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nErina Mano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 n\u00e0ng WAGs n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng nh\u1ea5t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. C\u00f4 v\u00e0 Shibasaki quen bi\u1ebft qua l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi quen v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian y\u00eau nhau, 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00edt g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i y\u00eau xa v\u00ec Gaku Shibasaki \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Mano v\u00e0 Shibasaki \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00ednh h\u00f4n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u00f4n l\u1ec5 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Erina Mano d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen cho ch\u1ed3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u00f4 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00edt n\u00f3i, gi\u00e0u ngh\u1ecb l\u1ef1c, th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n qua h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u1eef di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean 27 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00f4 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u1ed3ng. \"T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp ni\u1ec1m vui, ti\u1ebfng c\u01b0\u1eddi\", Mano n\u00f3i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGaku Shibasaki sinh n\u0103m 1992, hi\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Colombia \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nErina Mano sinh n\u0103m 1991, h\u01a1n ch\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ed5i. C\u00f4 l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. C\u00f4 t\u1eebng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 phim There's No Easy Job in This World, We Married as Job Romaji. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t khi tham gia c\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m phim 18+ nh\u01b0 Minna! Esper Dayo!...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f4 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ca s\u0129 v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u album nh\u1ea1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tour di\u1ec5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0103n kh\u00e1ch. S\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt 1,59 m, Erina Mano v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1ea5t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1edd g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t xinh \u0111\u1eb9p, th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i thu h\u00fat v\u00e0 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4344","checkdouble":"191522"},{"date":"15:13 18/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn '\u0111\u00e0n anh' \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u01b0ng anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng\u00a0v\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, kinh nghi\u1ec7m m\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>V\u00ec th\u1ebf, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u2018\u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i\u2019 V\u0103n L\u00e2m trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng: \u201cKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea5y b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00ec th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 sang Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Anh L\u00e2m hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i ch\u00ednh th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i anh \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ea5y!\u201d.<o:p></o:p><br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh th\u1ee9 3 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n) s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 3-7/8 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 xem ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-quan-hlv-quang-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-dang-van-lam-168-189294.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/bi-cam-quan-hlv-quang-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-dang-van-lam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-quan-hlv-quang-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-dang-van-lam-168-189294.html\">B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, HLV Qu\u1ea3ng Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 chi\u1ec1u 22/6, CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u2018c\u01b0a \u0111i\u1ec3m\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng FC c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-nhan-mua-loi-khen-sau-tran-gap-sai-gon-fc-168-187731.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-nhan-mua-loi-khen-sau-tran-gap-sai-gon-fc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-nhan-mua-loi-khen-sau-tran-gap-sai-gon-fc-168-187731.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</span><br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4343","checkdouble":"191517"},{"date":"17:13 18/07","title":"Quy\u1ebft theo nghi\u1ec7p HLV, Henry nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y Wenger","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/quyet-theo-nghiep-hlv-henry-nhan-loi-canh-bao-tu-thay-wenger.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Arsene Wenger kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Thierry Henry s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i hy sinh, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea5n th\u00e2n v\u00e0o con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n.</h2><div>B\u1ec9 k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. Chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c \"th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u00f3 l\u01a1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u1eeb HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Thierry Henry.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Wenger c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Henry khi l\u00e0m HLV chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Wenger c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Henry khi l\u00e0m HLV chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/quyet-theo-nghiep-hlv-henry-nhan-loi-canh-bao-tu-thay-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Henry khi l\u00e0m HLV\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, Henry c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin d\u1ea5n th\u00e2n v\u00e0o con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sau hai n\u0103m h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7c cho Martinez. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0i Sky Sports l\u00e0m c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o ngh\u1ec1 tay ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Henry c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Arsene Wenger, khi Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 b\u1ed9c b\u1ea1ch nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi chia tay Arsenal sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3:</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i hy sinh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 v\u00ec c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi xunh quanh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ch\u00ednh gia \u0111\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i khi\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecd bu\u1ed3n ch\u00e1n, ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u00edch k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft quan t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u1ebft ngo\u00e0i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\"</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u Thierry Henry hay Patrick Vieira c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng HLV gi\u1ecfi hay kh\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00f3. H\u1ecd th\u00f4ng minh, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 d\u00e1m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn hy sinh, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00e1m \u1ea3nh c\u1ea3 trong gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7?\"</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup: Ch\u1edd nh\u00e9 EURO 2020!</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup n\u0103m nay, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1eafc n\u00e9t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4342","checkdouble":"191531"},{"date":"12:32 18/07","title":"Real Madrid s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cristiano Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Antonio Cassano ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i 30 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; th\u00e0nh Turin</span> v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m, h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/m\u00f9a.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/ronaldo-se-hoi-han-voi-quyet-dinh-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Juventus m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Serie A v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd n\u00f3i chung ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Antonio Cassano th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 100% c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ronaldo v\u1ed1n d\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1eb5n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00fd ch\u00ed, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Real Madrid v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Raul, Ronaldo &lsquo;b\u00e9o&rsquo; hay David Beckham, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0 c\u1edb g\u00ec m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng thi\u1ebfu CR7 h\u1ebft c\u1ea3.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Juventus c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Ronaldo c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y may m\u1eafn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi Allegri.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf Juventus v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean IC Cup t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bayern Munich, Benfica, MLS All-Stars v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (ng\u00e0y 4/8).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e1m b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 cho m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo: C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n</span><br>\r\n100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo nghe t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4341","checkdouble":"191509"},{"date":"14:42 18/07","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay Real Madrid?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/theo-hernandez-sap-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Theo Hernandez s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Theo Hernandez s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Theo Hernandez s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Theo Hernandez s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/theo-hernandez-sap-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Theo Hernandez s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2017, CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i Theo Hernandez t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Atletico Madrid. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Theo Hernandez \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i CLB Alaves theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Anh ra s\u00e2n 38 tr\u1eadn, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid, sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh Marcelo v\u00e0 Nacho khi\u1ebfn Theo hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 13 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 23 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cho Los Blancos.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Theo Hernandez r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a HLV Julen Lopetegui. Tuy nhi\u00ean Real c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u1ebd g\u00e0i th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Morata cho Juventus.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cristiano Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Antonio Cassano ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay-180-191502.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay-180-191502.html\">James Rodriguez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nR\u1eddi Bernabeu 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\">N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4340","checkdouble":"191512"},{"date":"16:30 18/07","title":"N\u1ebfu Ronaldo l\u00e0 Nadal, Messi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Federer","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t Rafael Nadal v\u00e0 Roger Federer \u0111\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua. H\u1ecd chia nhau m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ai h\u01a1n ai. \u0110\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 qua tu\u1ed5i 30 song Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi v\u1eabn ghi t\u1edbi 44 v\u00e0 45 b\u00e0n cho Real v\u00e0 Barca trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb Real Madrid chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, so s\u00e1nh Nadal v\u00e0 Federer h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, so s\u00e1nh Nadal v\u00e0 Federer h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Cassano-phat-bieu-ve-Ronaldo-va-Messi,-so-sanh-Nadal-va-Federer-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 10 n\u0103m qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eebng mong mu\u1ed1n con trai m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a CR7 quay v\u1ec1 khi anh \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Nadal v\u00e0 Federer</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real, Antonio Cassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. Anh d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng tay v\u1ee3t v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i Nadal v\u00e0 Federer \u0111\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi. \u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch Messi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ronaldo m\u00e0 theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t\u201d, Cassano n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Vanity Fair.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cassano lap cu dup vao luoi doi bong cu.\" title=\"Cassano l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2014/3/cassano-4146-1394990785-20143176210.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi v\u00e0 so s\u00e1nh h\u1ecd v\u1edbi Nadal v\u00e0 Federer</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 nh\u01b0 Messi. Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. T\u00f4i th\u00edch qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Ronaldo gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Nadal, m\u1ed9t v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi gi\u1ed1ng Federer h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi kia. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i th\u00edch Messi b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ee9ng y\u00ean. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n bung qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Lionel.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bu-nhin-cua-messi-tai-argentina-chinh-thuc-bi-bay-ghe-421-191266.html\">B\u00f9 nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a Messi t\u1ea1i Argentina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb bay gh\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-chung-ket-hlv-phap-lo-ngai-tai-nang-cua-luka-modric-421-191226.html\">HLV Ph\u00e1p: S\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Modric th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Messi v\u00e0 Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-se-khien-messi-ronaldo-va-neymar-tro-nen-loi-thoi-421-191206.html\">Mbappe s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Messi, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Neymar tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-wc-lionel-messi-sau-tat-ca-mau-anh-chon-van-la-mau-dan-toc-471-191125.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi: Lionel Messi, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, m\u00e0u anh ch\u1ecdn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u00e0u d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-doi-bong-nhat-ban-chinh-thuc-mua-dut-messi-thai-lan-168-191109.html\">N\u00f3ng: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u2018Messi Th\u00e1i Lan\u2019</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4339","checkdouble":"191515"},{"date":"17:46 18/07","title":"G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nGareth Bale<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Bernabeu &ndash; Cris Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Bale vs Lopetegui v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Bale l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 16 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. B\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real. Nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 g\u00f3p 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Real-Madrid-cua-HLV-Lopetegui-4-cai-ten-du-bao-toa-sang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a CR7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh &ndash; khi nh\u1eefng Neymar, Mbappe hay Hazard c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa v\u1eddi (v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp). B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Gareth Bale s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Bale ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, thay v\u00ec \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Man United. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\">MU s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Gareth Bale t\u1eeb Real Madrid, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales n\u1ebfu Los Blancos quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dani Ceballos<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ti\u1ec3u Iniesta c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, anh kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Casemiro, Toni Kroos v\u00e0 Luka Modric. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Mateo Kovacic trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Julen Lopetegui, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u01b0a th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ceballos. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Trong 6 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i m\u00e0u \u00e1o U12 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n &ndash; v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ecdi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ceballos\" title=\"Ceballos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/ceba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ceballos s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Marco Asensio<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 32 tr\u1eadn La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ghi 6 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 6 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, d\u00f9 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Real, Marco Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Cris Ronaldo. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 r\u00ea d\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Asensio &ndash; nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng trong, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Zidane th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Asensio nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c trong hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &ndash; ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi H\u00f9m x\u00e1m Bayern. V\u1edbi th\u00f3i quen \u01b0a d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb, Asensio s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Asensio\" title=\"tien ve Asensio\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/12/asensio-thua-nhan-kha-nang-roi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Asensio r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>James Rodriguez<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay-180-191502.html\" target=\"_blank\">ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra</span>. Anh v\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nhau c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 tu\u1ea7n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, d\u00f9 James v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3, phong c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n n\u1ebfu anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i, s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa anh c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Real Madrid &ndash; v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi \u0111i khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zidane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez se chong lai doi bong cu cua minh\" title=\"James Rodriguez s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem James l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Asensio gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Isco, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u00f4i sao bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cristiano Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Antonio Cassano ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\">N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4338","checkdouble":"191534"},{"date":"15:21 18/07","title":"Rooney tin M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Man City m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/rooney-phat-bieu-ve-mu-va-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng anh t\u1eebng c\u00f3 13 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Man City \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2012/13.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18, Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Premier League. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00f2n, b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 Man United t\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola c\u00f2n l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Man City c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Arsenal. Tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, M.U c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tay tr\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng Romelu Lukaku, Alexis Sanchez, Nemanja Matic hay Victor Lindelof.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/10/Wayne-Rooney-phat-bieu-ve-MU-se-gianh-chuc-vo-dich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSang h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng khi mang v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Lee Grant. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Rooney tin M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWayne Rooney t\u1eebng c\u00f3 13 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton v\u00e0 m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang M\u1ef9 ch\u01a1i cho DC United. C\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Premier League 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U vo doi\" title=\"M.U vo doi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/rooney-phat-bieu-ve-mu-va-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c b\u1edfi Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3\u201d, Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U tr\u00ean BBC Sport. \u201c\u1ede b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u g\u00ec nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 Man City m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u n\u1eefa s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-yeu-to-chi-ra-ronaldo-nen-chon-mu-thay-vi-den-juventus-172-191429.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra Ronaldo n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn M.U thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia-172-191421.html\">M.U chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-alexis-sanchez-chua-the-tham-du-tour-du-dau-cung-mu-172-191407.html\">V\u00ec sao Alexis Sanchez ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ivan-perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-mu-cua-mourinho-172-191400.html\">Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi M.U c\u1ee7a Mourinho?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4337","checkdouble":"191513"},{"date":"15:03 18/07","title":"T\u00e2m th\u01b0 Daley Blind g\u1eedi Man Utd sau khi ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/tam-thu-daley-blind-gui-man-utd-sau-khi-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind sau khi chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Ajax Amsterdam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, Daley Blind quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo-172-191388.html\">chia tay Man Utd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Ajax Amsterdam</span>.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, MU v\u00e0 Ajax \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cg\u1eedi tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d n\u00e0y, c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 giao d\u1ecbch \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1m ph\u00e1t. Blind tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Amsterdam v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 70.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau khi r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Daley Blind vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau khi r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/tam-thu-daley-blind-gui-man-utd-sau-khi-ra-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Daley Blind vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau khi r\u1eddi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Instagram, Blind \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi MU v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung nh\u01b0 sau: \"L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o bi\u1ebft bao khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh Manchester United.\"<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed nh\u01b0 v\u1eady qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi 4 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 - c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00e1c HLV, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u1eadu c\u1ea7n, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.\"<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00ec t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, s\u1ebd m\u00e3i nh\u1edb 'Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1'! Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 r\u1ed3i.\"<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4336","checkdouble":"191514"},{"date":"16:36 18/07","title":"Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i thay Karius. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nen liverpool 2\" title=\"N\u1ec1n liverpool 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>So s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nLoris Karius (Liverpool)</h2>\r\n<p><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 1.63</strong><strong><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 10</strong><strong><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 68.89%</strong><strong><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 27.42 (67.18%)</strong><strong><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 0</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jurgen Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Simon Mignolet v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Loris Karius sau phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/5/Chelsea-muon-mua-Alisson-Nen-hay-khong-nen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Karius \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Karius gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5/7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap The Kop c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018 v\u1edbi Real c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2018, nh\u00ecn chung m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Karius \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 10/19 tr\u1eadn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Karius ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf 14/38 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 Liverpool ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u1edf Premier League 2017/18. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Karius b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Alisson, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKarius gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 53% s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Alisson ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 46% s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Serie A (17/37). V\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat (80,1% c\u1ee7a Alisson so v\u1edbi 68,98% c\u1ee7a Karius).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, Alisson l\u1ea1i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Karius (4 so v\u1edbi 0). Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 1,63 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Roma l\u00ean t\u1edbi 2,89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<h2>Jordan Pickford (Everton)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 3.18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 10</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 67.42%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 25.46 (44.49%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 5</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford t\u1eeb Sunderland, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pickford khien doi khach khong the co ban thang\" title=\"Pickford khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/11/MU-nham-thu-mon-Jordan-Pickford-thay-De-Gea-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pickford ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Sau \u0111\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018 khi gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18, Pickford c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 trung b\u00ecnh 3.18 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi Alisson (2.89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat). Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i 58 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng, cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma (28).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pickford ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 67,42%, khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh 80,1% c\u1ee7a Alisson. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Pickford c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 44,49%, k\u00e9m h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u con s\u1ed1 79,7% c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Pickford cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Alisson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<h2>Thibaut Courtois (Chelsea)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 2.17</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 15</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 68.52%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 28.09 (70.4%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-dung-tien-de-bep-liverpool-vu-alisson-172-191489.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/thibaut-courtois-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Alisson&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 35 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn 38 b\u00e0n thua, cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 28 b\u00e0n thua sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Alisson. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Alisson gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Serie A 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 68,52%, song v\u1eabn th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 80,1% c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Roma.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Alisson \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ec9 m\u1eafc 1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil b\u00ean ph\u00eda Roma l\u00e0 4.</div>\r\n<h2>Ederson (Man City)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 1.63</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 16</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 68.29%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 26.14 (85.34%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 6</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEderson \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil anh l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Alisson. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Ederson\" title=\"thu mon Ederson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/Thu-mon-Ederson-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Man-City--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Ederson kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEderson ra s\u00e2n 37 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Alisson trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Man City gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 16 l\u1ea7n th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Roma gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17 l\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlisson ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 27 b\u00e0n thua sau 37 tr\u1eadn, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng (28 b\u00e0n thua sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n). V\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Ederson cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Alisson (85,34% so v\u1edbi 79.7%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Ederson, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, cao h\u01a1n 4 c\u1ee7a Alisson.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David De Gea (MU)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 3.11</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 80.28%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 25.46 (57.54%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 3</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDavid de Gea l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a danh hi\u1ec7u &ldquo;G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng&rdquo; Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, duy nh\u1ea5t De Gea cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Alisson.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho xac nhan De Gea bat chinh tai chung ket FA Cup\" title=\"Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn De Gea b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft FA Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a De Gea v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee9 qua 90 ph\u00fat th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 3.11 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat con s\u1ed1 2.89 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. C\u1ea3 De Gea v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (18 so v\u1edbi 17).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a De Gea l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80.28%, cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi 80.1% c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda Roma. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u1ec9 m\u1eafc 3 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Alisson l\u00e0 4.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 De Gea b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Alisson \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c (57.54% so v\u1edbi 79.7%), nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi M.U d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Hugo Lloris (Tottenham)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 2.39</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 15</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 70.09%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 27.67 (75.2%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 8</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHugo Lloris l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Tottenham trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lloris phat bieu ve viec Real gianh ve vao Top 4 Ngoai hang Anh\" title=\"Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/10/hugo-lloris-vao-top-4-tot-hon-viec-gianh-1-danh-hieu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lloris gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15 tr\u1eadn \u1edf NHA 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra s\u00e2n 36 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15 l\u1ea7n, k\u00e9m 2 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Alisson \u1edf Roma. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Lloris c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Lloris c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 2.39 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 70.09%, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Alisson l\u00e0 2.89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 80.1%. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Spurs c\u0169ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat (75,2% so v\u1edbi 78,9%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua \u1edf Premier League 2017/18, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m trong Top 5 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i so v\u1edbi Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4335","checkdouble":"191526"},{"date":"16:51 18/07","title":"3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-van-de-can-mourinho-giai-quyet-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong top 6. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t hay s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2018/19.</h2><h2>T\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft b\u00e1m bi\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Man United. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Antonio Valencia chuy\u1ec3n sang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 chia c\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuan Mata l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t m\u1ea5y n\u0103m qa. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1eaft v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU c\u1ea7n Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU c\u1ea7n Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/17/3-van-de-cua-MU-can-Mourinho-giai-quyet-o-mua-giai-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man United \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft b\u00e1m bi\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 Hirving Lozano. C\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia v\u00e0 Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Tuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trung t\u00e2m. V\u1eady n\u00ean, Mourinho s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<h2>Chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro\" title=\"Alex Sandro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/mu-tu-choi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alex Sandro \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang ng\u00e0n c\u00e2n treo s\u1ee3i t\u00f3c. Ashley Young \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Man United c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay m\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt c\u1ea7n m\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nYoung l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd. V\u00e0 Mourinho th\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00e1 k\u00edn nh\u1eefng l\u1ed1i v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a De Gea n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League theo l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex Sandro l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Sandro \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u1edf Juventus. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Man United.</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00fap Pogba v\u00e0 Martial ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Martial\" title=\"Pogba Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/164824-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Martial ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u0103n tr\u1edf su\u1ed1t hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pogba. Nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Pogba c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf World Cup 2018 ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Mourinho ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd. C\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng Man United. V\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Fred h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, Pogba s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu m\u00f9a sau, Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup, v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Martial \u0111ang d\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh sau khi Alexis Sanchez c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford. Ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc n\u1ebfu anh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man United v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. V\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00e0nh cho Mourinho l\u00e0 Martial s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Marcus Rashford cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\">MU s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-lam-dieu-nay-de-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-ivan-perisic-172-191494.html\">MU l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ivan Perisic</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4334","checkdouble":"191528"},{"date":"17:38 18/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/18/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard 3 l\u00fd do tin Real s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard 3 l\u00fd do tin Real s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</span>, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 James Rodriguez t\u1edbi Bayern Munich theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Real ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ra \u0111i, NHM Real \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMbappe v\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111\u00f2i 400 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Neymar v\u00e0 290 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Mbappe, Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y. Los Blancos s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng NHM.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, Real mua Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea lo l\u1eafng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf Stamford Bridge. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 n\u00ean r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 hay kh\u00f4ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m m\u00ecnh, Hazard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng CLB v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n duy tr\u00ec tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 anh \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Real \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn tr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2020, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Real \u00e9p gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" title=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/chelsea-tu-choi-loi-de-nghi-dau-tien-cua-real-cho-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 27, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u00edn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Hazard r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00eam l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu Chelsea bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u1edf m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real Madrid d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Hazard, HLV Sarri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGareth Bale (Real Madrid), Leon Bailey (Bayer Leverkusen) v\u00e0 Anthony Martial \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm thay Hazard, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi, 48 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 kh\u1edfi tranh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng 20 ng\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard. N\u1ebfu anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i, The Blues c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, qua \u0111\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1edbm b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. \u00c1p l\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Real th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4333","checkdouble":"191533"}]}